dct_description_sm: Inset map: Umgebungen von Brüssel. Includes 8 drawings of facades of buildings: "Grössenverhaeltniss der Haupt-Gebäude in Brüssel." Appears to be based on the 1837 map of the Society for the Diffusion of Useful Knowledge, London. "Meyers Handatlas (Suplm. 9) No. 109."
dct_publisher_sm: Hildburghausen ; Philadelphia : Geographische Graviranstalt, Bibliographisches Institut, [1860?]
